Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还这么死脑筋  真让我倍感安慰\NWell, it's good to know you're still dumb as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有些事是不会变的\NYeah, well, some things never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你怎么跟同类挥起砍刀来了\NNow, why are you getting into machete fights with your own kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}昆丁  我来找的那家伙\NQuentin, the one I came for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们原是一个巢穴的\NWe were in the same nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在追杀转化我的那个吸血鬼  我的创造者\NI'm hunting the vampire who turned me, my maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不要误会\NWell, now, don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我支持你杀他  可是为什么\NI'm down with the hunting, but, uh...why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}先下手为强\NKill him before he kills me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}免得我再遭殃\Nagain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}棒极了\NAwesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你还没下班\NUh, if you're still on the clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}118的女士说她的水槽堵了\Nlady in 118 says the sink's backed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么回事\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在这里做什么\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就知道你这人不对劲\NI knew there was something off about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那堆吓人的陆海军装备  还有鬓角\Nwith your creepy Army-Navy and your sideburns --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}停下\NStop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在帮你修水槽\NUm, I'm fixing your sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我和昆丁是老朋友了\NQuentin and I went way back --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是老爸最喜欢的一个  仅次于我\None of the old man's favorites, next to me, it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听听这个\NListen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"水瓶座纪元二号  0800"\N"Age of Aquarius II, 0800,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}后面还有数字  都划掉了\Nand then there's some other numbers all crossed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有些奇怪的名字  "大美人鱼"\NSome other weird names here, too -- the Big Mermaid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"红心大战"  也都划掉了\NSolitaire -- it's all crossed out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}除了这一个  "幸运玛拉"\Nexcept this one -- the Lucky Myra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是游艇\NYachts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}游艇的名字  幸运玛拉  水瓶座纪元二号\NNames of yachts -- Lucky Myra, Age of Aquarius II.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你看这个  "洄见"多了三点水\NLook at this one -- Sea You Later, spelled s-e-a.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该懂了吧\NI mean, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是出航时间\NSo, then these are launch times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有目的地\NAnd what -- destinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错  但这些艇都不会靠港了\NMm-hmm. Except none of them ever get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}幸运玛拉昨天下午起航\NThe Lucky Myra left yesterday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可以保证它已经遭袭了\NI guarantee you it's already been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"遭袭"是什么意思\NWhat do you mean, "hit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}强行登船  焚毁  葬身海底\NBoarded, burned, and buried at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是我们巢穴用餐的方式\NMy nest -- that's how we fed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一向如此\NHow we always fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们养着一只小舰队  大概有六艘船\NWe kept a tight little fleet, maybe a half-dozen boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}外表并不招摇  只是普通游船\NNothing ostentatious, just pleasure craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我航行的里程都够绕美洲十圈了\NI must have circled the Americas 10 times during my tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有人专门扮成外乡人  在港口游荡\NA few of us would act as stringers and patrol the harbors,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}寻找合适的目标\Nlooking for the right-size target --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那些驶向很远的港口的豪华游轮\Nfat, rich yachts going to far-off ports.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}记录下游轮的名字和目的地\NTake down the boat's name and destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}再用无线电通知水上的同伴\Nradio it to the crew in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后我们就...\NAnd then we just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让海水淹没我们的罪行\Nlet the ocean swallow up all our sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们是吸血鬼海盗\NVampire pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}原来你们是干这个的\NThat's what you guys are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}吸血海盗\NVampirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们一起干了这么多年\NYou know, all the years we ran together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}居然从没有人想到过\NI can't believe nobody ever thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说什么啊  这个很容易想到啊\NWhat do you mean? It's like the third thing you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}才不是呢\NNo, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  你的创造者\NAll right, so, y-your maker
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}准备在这附近觅食对吗\Nis set up to feed around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们该怎么找\NWell, what are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他生活一向很有范儿\NWell, he likes to live in style.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他通常合法租下房屋\NHe usually rents legitimately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}偏远而临海的地方\NAlways remote, always coastal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可能是个小岛\NSo an island, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是有线电视收费单\NYou got a cable bill here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}昆丁还包月了美国棒球联盟\NHmm. Quentin's got the NFL package.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}普兰提斯岛\NPrentiss Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听说过吗\NHeard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}既然你是创造者的心头肉\NYeah, so, if you were your maker's favorite,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他为什么要杀死你\Nwhy did he kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当你被转化的时候\NWhen you get turned,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就像你重新生在了一个吸血鬼巢穴中\Nit's like you're reborn into a vampire nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的创造者就是你的全部\NYour maker -- he means everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你会开始相信他就是上帝\NI mean, you really start believing he's God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你的创造者也是这么想的话\NNow, if your maker happens to believe the same thing, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就成了问题了\NSee how that could be a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你非要现在吸那个东西吗\Nyou really have to do that? I mean, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起  兄弟\NI'm sorry, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我感觉好多了  但还在恢复\NI'm better, but I'm still on the mend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们的父亲  他嫉妒心很重\NAnyway...our father -- he was a jealous God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他让家族成员住在一起\NHe kept the family together
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在海上漂泊  远离外面的世界\Nbut kept us apart from the rest of the world, always at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我做事一向以家族为先\NI always did what was best for the nest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直到我遇见了她\Ntill I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安德莉亚\NAndrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安德莉亚・科莫斯\NAndrea Kormos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她真美\NBeautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那种无以言表的美  你懂吗\NI mean, words don't even cut it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}希腊的名门之后\NGreek, heiress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她驾一艘单桅帆船前往加那利群岛\NShe was sailing a 42-foot sloop to the Canary Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我本该把她的目的地告诉我的同伴\NNow, I should have called her boat's destination in to my crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我却跟她上了船\Nbut instead, I joined her on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真的吗\NSeriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这算是什么三俗的桥段啊\NWas Fabio on the cover of that paperback?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的生活从此因她而变  迪恩\NMy life changed when she entered it, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在那之前我所做的一切\NEverything I had been or done up to that point just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}似乎都消失了\Nseemed to vanish...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只剩下了我和她\NInto what we had become together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们找到了真爱  伙计\NI mean... We found it, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最后  我们在路易斯安那定居\NEventually, we settled in Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后有天晚上  我们回到家\NAnd then one night, we were coming home,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}老爸就在那儿等我\Nand the old man -- he was just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有我的旧友昆丁  索兰托\NQuentin, Sorento, my oldest nestmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直到那天晚上我才明白\NIt was only that night I understood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的离开  在他看来多么不可饶恕\Nwhat a crime it was to him -- me leaving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们把我按在地上  接着斩首\NThey pinned me down, and they beheaded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看到的最后一幕\NThe last thing I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是他咬破安德莉亚的喉咙\Nwas the old man tearing out Andrea's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}报复不就是这样吗\NWell, that's what payback's all about -- am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}到码头了\NDocks are up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}应该能找到能用的小船\NShould be able to find a dinghy to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快到了\NWe're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在抓吸血鬼  老巢在普兰提斯岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}想到什么了吗\NRemind you of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}删除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}回到这个世界突然感觉怪怪的\NIt's weird being back -- in the world, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是吗\NIsn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NSure as hell is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是怎么面对这一切的\NI mean, what do you do with it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所有这一切\NAll the -- all the everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我都不知道这世界是不是真的\NHell, I don't even know if this world is real,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是不是真的\Nif I'm real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听我说\NHey, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我十分清楚这种心态的后果\NI see what happens down that rabbit hole, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们是真的\NWe're real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  这一切都是真的\NBenny, this is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要活下去必须这么想  懂了吗\NIt's the only way to play this game, you get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该走了  本尼\NTime to move, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}老爸的大键琴\NThe old man's harpsichord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼\NBenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  不\NNo, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼\NBenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安德莉亚\NAndrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}傻子\NIdiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}想让我再杀你一次吗\NGonna make me do this all over again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你好  索兰托\NHello, Sorento.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他转化了你\NHe turned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在有点忙\NLittle busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩二号备用手机\NThis is Dean's other, other cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道该怎么做\Nso you must know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}德州驾照  艾米利亚・理查德森
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就是干这个的\NSo, that's what you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟踪无助的妇女\NYou stalk helpless women
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}闯入她们的房间然后修她们的水管\Nand you break into their motel room and you fix their plumbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.99,0:24:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么要修我的水槽\NWhy are you fixing my sink?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为有人丢了一大堆酸橙进去塞住了水管\NWell, because somebody jammed about 800 limes down the drain...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}损坏了清理器\Nand blew out the disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  别碰我的东西\NOh. Right. Don't touch the produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不是要离开小镇吗\NI thought you were leaving town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  我只是在帮着旅馆做维修\NI am. I'm just helping out with maintenance at the motel,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.69,0:24:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}埃弗雷特他爸生病了\Nyou know, while Everett's dad is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谁是埃弗雷特\NWho's Everett?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你来这儿多久了\NHow long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}三个月  怎么了\NThree months. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一般人来到一个小镇\NWell, you know, usually when someone moves into a town,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.76,0:24:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都会住到镇子里去\Nthey actually, uh, you know, move into the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.51,0:24:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也是啊\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}汽车旅馆可不算是小镇的一部分\NA motel is not actually part of the town that it's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.23,0:24:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}它那儿都不算\NIt's not part of anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还没找到地方\NWell, I haven't found a place yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我为什么要跟你解释\NWhy am I explaining myself to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.51,0:24:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是个流浪汉或者杂务工\NYou're a drifter or a handyman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.40,0:24:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想我该走了\NI-I think I should just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.58,0:24:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  我觉得你该离开了\NYeah, I think you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.07,0:25:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你好\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.90,0:25:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}干什么\NOkay, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.89,0:25:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-什么  -你为什么打电话给我\N- What? - Why did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么你小声说话\NWhy are you whispering?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.73,0:25:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}解释起来有点复杂\NIt's kind of hard to explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我正忙着清理吸血鬼老巢呢\Nbut I'm sort of in the middle of cleaning out a vampire's nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.58,0:25:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我情势有点不利\Nand it's sort of gone a little sideways on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.57,0:25:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么  你是白痴吗  迪恩\NWhat?! Are you an idiot, Dean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.99,0:25:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还没笨到一个人去吸血鬼老巢吧\NYou know better than to go into a vamp nest alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.51,0:25:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是一个人  该死\NI'm not alone, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.00,0:25:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行了吗  我不是一个人\NAll right? I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.43,0:25:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有支援\NI've got backup --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.52,0:25:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那家伙追查这伙人有一阵了\Nguy who's been tracking the nest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.06,0:25:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}哪个家伙  盖思吗\NWhat guy? Garth?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.88,0:25:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么  不  你不认识\NWhat? No. You don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.96,0:25:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是个朋友\NHe's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.00,0:25:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}朋友  迪恩  你没有任何...\NA friend? Dean, you don't have any --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.81,0:25:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你所有的朋友都死了\Nall your friends are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.05,0:25:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我打电话不是想跟你说这些\NThat's not what I called to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}索兰托  去  告诉老爸是真的\NSorento, go. Tell the old man it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.27,0:25:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他听你的\NHe listens to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.04,0:25:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}已经很久了\NIt's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.93,0:25:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}比起索兰托  我们的父亲更相信我的判断\NOur father has come to trust my judgment over Sorento's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.46,0:25:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只听命于他\NI answer only to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.21,0:26:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和上帝上床必然是有好处的\NWell, sleeping with God has got to have some perks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.08,0:26:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}的确\NYes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.80,0:26:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}去看看老爸还需要什么\NMake sure the old man has everything he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.77,0:26:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼\NOh, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.17,0:26:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听到你回来了的时候\NWhen I heard you were back --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.02,0:26:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不知道为什么  我就知道是真的\NI don't know -- somehow, I knew it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.77,0:26:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只能相信  期冀\NI had to believe it, to hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.07,0:26:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安德莉亚  发生了什么\NAndrea, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.01,0:26:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}老爸说他要吸干你的血\NThe old man said he was gonna bleed you dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.57,0:26:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.49,0:26:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他改主意了\NHe changed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.55,0:26:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我昏了过去\NI blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.05,0:26:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}醒来时  我正从他手腕处吸血\NWhen I woke up, I was drinking from his wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.31,0:26:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.84,0:27:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这一切都是因为我  对不起\NAll this is because of me. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.85,0:27:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是  这不怪你\NNo. It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.41,0:27:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  你从未对我有任何隐瞒\NYou never hid anything from me, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.60,0:27:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是我选择了你\NI chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.69,0:27:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但你为什么留下\NBut why'd you stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.09,0:27:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和他们在一起  和他一起\Nwith them, with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.40,0:27:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.25,0:27:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你也记得最初的情形\NYou remember what it's like at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.50,0:27:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最初  一切都重新开始\NFirst, everything resets.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.14,0:27:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}活着就是吸血\NLife is blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.47,0:27:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那就是全部\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.59,0:27:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-不管是谁给了你血...  -我懂\N- And whoever gives it to you... - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.26,0:27:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这很复杂\NIt's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.79,0:27:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么事都很复杂\NEvery damn thing is complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.04,0:27:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也不一定非得如此\NIt doesn't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.57,0:27:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安德莉亚\NAndrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.21,0:27:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  我没法杀死他  我们都不行\NBenny, I can't kill him -- none of us can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.36,0:27:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是你  你死而复生\NBut you -- you came back from the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.69,0:27:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你证明了他不是万能的\NYou're proof that he's not all-powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.64,0:27:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他不是上帝\Nthat he's not God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.59,0:28:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  他怕你  我知道\NHe's scared of you, Benny -- I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.81,0:28:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道我回来是为了摧毁他的觅食方式\NYou understand that I came back to burn his operation to the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.04,0:28:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}阻止杀戮\Nto stop the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.24,0:28:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}做你要做的  我们就可以在一起了\NDo what you came for, and we can be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.86,0:28:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他要我们带本尼过去\NHe wants Benny brought to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.30,0:28:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道我们分开了一年\NI get the separate-lives thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.65,0:28:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但这可是猎魔\Nbut this is a hunting thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.18,0:28:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们得搞清这界限\Nand we need to find that line --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.48,0:28:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天啊  别说了  我已经把地点发给你了\NOh, my God, stop talking. I texted you my 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.69,0:28:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}收到了  我这就去\NYeah, I got it. Look, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.11,0:28:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  如果你们能处理好  那很好\NAnd, listen, if you handle it, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.73,0:28:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会请你朋友喝一轮酒\NI'll buy your friend the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.03,0:28:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是  迪恩  听我说\NBut, Dean, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.66,0:28:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩\NDean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.89,0:28:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩  你在听吗\NDean, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.29,0:28:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩  迪恩\NDean. Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.83,0:28:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在搞什么啊\NYou kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.11,0:29:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伙计  别这样\NOh, man, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.39,0:29:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该死的\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.08,0:29:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你好  父亲\NHello, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.11,0:29:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼\NBenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.16,0:29:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我无话可说\NI have no words.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.42,0:29:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别骗我了\NNow, I know that ain't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.14,0:29:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}能给我们解释一下吗\NCan you help us understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.06,0:29:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你不欠我们什么  但是\NI know you don't owe us anything, but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.32,0:29:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你怎么会活着  站在我面前呢\NHow are you here, standing in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.30,0:29:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我找到了一条回来的路\NI found a way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.20,0:29:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}从地狱吗\NFrom Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.38,0:29:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}据我所知  地狱在隔壁\NRight next door, as far as I could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.04,0:29:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}隔壁\NNext door?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.46,0:29:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是什么\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.28,0:29:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我大概只能让你亲眼见识了\NOh, I think I'll just have to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.60,0:30:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道这么说不能改变什么\NI know it won't change anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.64,0:30:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我很后悔杀了你\Nbut I regretted having you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.42,0:30:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一切结束之后\NWhen it was all done,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.15,0:30:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看着支离破碎的你  痛苦不已\NI wailed when I saw you in all those pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.70,0:30:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是不是  索兰托\NDidn't I, Sorento?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.38,0:30:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是不是哭得像世上最丑的孩子\NDidn't I wail like the ugliest baby in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.62,0:30:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  父亲\NYes, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.90,0:30:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}于是你决定转化他的婆娘\NThat's when you decided to turn his cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.39,0:30:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可怜的家伙充满怨念\NPoor so-so is bitter
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.31,0:30:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为你的"婆娘"地位比他高\Nbecause your "Cow" Outranks him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.43,0:30:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么不让她死\NWhy didn't you let her die?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.57,0:30:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她对你毫无意义\NShe meant nothing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.51,0:30:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但她是你的一切\NBut she meant everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.25,0:30:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果唯一能从我任性的儿子那里挽回的\NIf that's all I could salvage from my wayward son --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.92,0:30:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是那个你为其抵抗你创造者的女人\Nthe woman he defied his maker for --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.90,0:30:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想要个能让我记得你的人\NI wanted someone to remember you by.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.53,0:31:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你怎么会知道生活的价值\NWhat the hell do you know about the value of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.64,0:31:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是个吸血鬼\NYou're a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.66,0:31:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.70,0:31:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得我们都清楚\NAnd I think we both know
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.26,0:31:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谁的同类杀死了更多人类\Nwhich of our kinds kills more humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.12,0:31:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}从统计学来说  是你的\NWell, statistically speaking, that'd be your --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.96,0:31:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  谢谢你  小卡\NYes, thank you, Cass.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.06,0:31:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我懂\NI get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.58,0:31:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是担心如果我们上去了  我会做什么\NYou're worried what I might do if we make it topside.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.42,0:31:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怕我会吃你的小猪猪\NI'll start eating your little piggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.84,0:31:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我已经告诉过你  伙计  我被杀之前\NI already told you, man -- by the time I got iced,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.72,0:31:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一直严格靠输血和吸捐血为生\NI was strictly on blood transfusions, donated blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.04,0:31:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}的确不是捐给我的\NNot donated to me, I'll give you that,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.66,0:31:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我在黑市上花了大价钱买来的\Nbut I paid good black-market scratch for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.53,0:31:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是什么  吸血鬼节食法吗\NSo, what is that? Like the vampire zone diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.79,0:31:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  我想说的是\NLook, all I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.93,0:31:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我开始看到人性的光辉了\Nis I started seeing something in humanity, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.05,0:31:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看到一些不该被夺去的东西\NSomething that shouldn't be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.60,0:31:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我吸血  但不吸人\NI drink blood. I don't drink people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.49,0:31:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我为什么要信你\NAnd why the hell should I believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.75,0:31:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你信什么重要吗\NWhat does it matter what you believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.85,0:31:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就真那么蠢吗  迪恩\NYou got your head so far up your ass, Dean,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.38,0:31:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都不知道我们已经完了\Nyou don't even realize we're already done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.80,0:31:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天使知道\NThe angel knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.65,0:31:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}带着他这么惹眼的人  我们根本出不去\NWe are never gonna make it with him next to us glowing like a beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.22,0:31:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要我提醒你谈好的条件吗\NDo I need to remind you of our deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.65,0:31:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你承诺过的事\NOf what you committed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.56,0:31:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他会害死我们的\NHe is gonna get us killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.89,0:31:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或许有机会检验你的话了\NWe may get to test that theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.29,0:32:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-又有怪物  -是利维坦\N- More monsters? - Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.81,0:32:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么你不飞走\NWhy don't you blip out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.68,0:32:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}它们太近了  我做不到\NThey're too close. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.05,0:32:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快跑\NRun.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.83,0:32:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  别去  狗狗  狗狗\NNo, no, no. Dog, dog, dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.11,0:32:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不要  狗狗  别烦那位愤怒的小姐了\NOh, no, dog, don't bother the...angry lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.70,0:32:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真抱歉\NUh, hey, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.53,0:32:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"狗狗"  你就这么叫它\N"Dog"? That's what you're calling him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.16,0:32:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}的确名副其实\NWell, it's accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.42,0:32:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}狗狗在打抗生素吗\NIs Dog taking his antibiotics?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.20,0:32:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  没错\NUh, yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.97,0:33:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}它好多了  谢谢\NHe's doing much better. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.32,0:33:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我得说\NYou know, um, I have to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.12,0:33:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我见过不少缝合的伤口\NI've seen a lot of stitches in my time,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.44,0:33:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的技术真不错\Nand you've got really good hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.03,0:33:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.95,0:33:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对了  你觉得我很可怕吗\NSo, you think I'm creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.77,0:33:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的衣服都在军需用品店买  这是很可怕\NI think it's creepy you buy all your clothing at army surplus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}白人至上主义者就这样\NWhite supremacists do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.58,0:33:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说得对  可我不是\NYeah, but I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.79,0:33:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}四处流窜的连环杀手也这样\NDrifting serial killers do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.08,0:33:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有道理\NFair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.93,0:33:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就这么凭空出现  又行踪不定\NYou come from nowhere, you appear to be going nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.77,0:33:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还"见过很多缝合的伤口"\Nand you've "Seen a lot of stitches."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.73,0:33:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些都绝对让人毛骨悚然\NIt's all pretty solid creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.10,0:33:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你也不知道该何去何从  不是吗\NYou have no idea where you're going, either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.04,0:33:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.02,0:33:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是很清楚\NNot really.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.45,0:34:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是因为你没有可依靠的人\NAnd that's because you have no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.61,0:34:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无牵无挂  对吗\NI mean, at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.60,0:34:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以你才会在这个地方\NI mean, that's why you're... here in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.99,0:34:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有过一个牵挂的人\NI used to -- have someone, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.31,0:34:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不过都过去了\NBut that's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.19,0:34:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都结束了\NIt's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.37,0:34:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你对此也有体会  不是吗\NYou know what that's like, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.36,0:34:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是迪恩的二号替补...\NThis is Dean's other, other...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.63,0:34:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我猜你的起死回生\NI suppose you coming back from the dead --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.42,0:34:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这绝对是叛变了  是不是\Nwell, that's the definition of mutiny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.00,0:34:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这事让我觉得很疲惫\NAll of this has me feeling so...tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.20,0:34:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你本该放我一马的\NYou should have let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.21,0:35:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可是本尼  我什么都不会放\NBut, Benny, I don't let things go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.75,0:35:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.91,0:35:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你活了这么久  却怎么几乎什么都没有\NYou lived so long, how is it you have so little, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.09,0:35:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只有一架老大键琴和一窝土狼\NNothing but a beat-up old harpsichord and nest of hyenas.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.34,0:35:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}大海是我的\NI have the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.78,0:35:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-我还有安德莉亚  -你没有\N- And I have Andrea. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.32,0:35:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你没得到她\NYou don't have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.23,0:35:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这我知道\NAt least that much I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.97,0:35:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个蠢娘们\NOh, that dumb bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.82,0:35:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你什么时候有了这种身手\NWhen the hell did you learn to fight like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.18,0:35:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}熟能生巧\NI've had a lot of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.28,0:35:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-你就打算这么坐着  -你说得对\N- You just gonna sit there? - You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.27,0:35:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在这儿待得太久了  本尼\NI've been here so, so long, Benny,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.17,0:35:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}见过的结局和花样不计其数\Nseen all the outcomes, all the patterns a trillion times.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.62,0:36:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}全都不值一提\NIt all means so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.99,0:36:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个世界就是座绝望的坟墓  没别的\NThis universe is a pyramid of despair, nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.36,0:36:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}挺悲观啊\NA little dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.24,0:36:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}毕竟  我是恶魔\NI am evil, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.77,0:36:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}至少我还有这点悲观保持我的本色\NAt least I've had that much to keep me cold at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.82,0:36:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你从来没有  是吗\NYou never had that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.71,0:36:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}凡事都要考虑  思量\NEverything had to be thought about, considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.85,0:36:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}苏格拉底有云\NYou know what Socrates said
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.27,0:36:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不加思考的人生不值得过\Nabout a life unconsidered.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.48,0:36:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.01,0:36:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但就我们的本性而言\NBut what we have in us?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.00,0:36:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  这不叫人生\NBenny, that's not life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.49,0:36:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这一点你还是不明白\NThat's what you still don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.81,0:36:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以你才总是痛不欲生\NThat's why it's always been so hard for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.47,0:36:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可怜的本杰明\Nmy poor Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.06,0:36:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}起来\NGet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.09,0:36:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是我唯一还能从你那儿夺走的东西\NThis is the one last thing I can take from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.76,0:36:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没门\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.32,0:36:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该死  你做点什么  再来杀我啊\NYou try, damn it. You try and kill me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.33,0:36:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你个小虫子  这是我的历史\NThis is my story, you gnat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.03,0:36:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}起来\NGet up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.01,0:36:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}结局由我来选择  不是你\NIt ends the way I choose, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.83,0:37:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}起码我能让你看点新鲜的了  老爸\NWell, at least I can finally show you something new, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.98,0:37:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个崭新的世界\NA whole new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.75,0:37:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}老爸死了\NThe old man is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.29,0:37:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.24,0:37:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}去哪儿  本尼\NWhere, Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.16,0:37:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说什么呢\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.82,0:37:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}去哪儿都行\NAnywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.80,0:37:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不想离开  对吗\NYou're not leaving here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.23,0:37:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你从没想要离开\NAnd you never were.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.32,0:37:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们这儿什么都不缺\NWe have everything we need right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.63,0:38:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这种觅食方式依然天衣无缝\NThe operation is still perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.66,0:38:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们可以扬帆公海  一同掳掠\NWe can ride the high seas, plunder together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.83,0:38:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们能过上梦寐以求的生活\NWe can have the life we always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.80,0:38:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只想把这儿烧成灰  一走了之\NWhat I wanted was to leave a burning crater behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.52,0:38:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}放下对你的回忆\NI wanted to put your memory to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.36,0:38:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不只是回忆\NBut I'm not a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.85,0:38:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  我就在你眼前\NBenny, I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.62,0:38:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我爱的女人\NWhat I loved --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.77,0:38:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}早已逝去\Nit ain't here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.86,0:38:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她早就被像我和如今的你这样的怪物\NIt was snuffed out a long time ago by monsters like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.96,0:38:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}扼杀了\Nlike what you've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.07,0:38:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得你现在比我强吗\NYou think you're better than me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.52,0:38:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.02,0:38:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得我们都该死\NI think we're all damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.39,0:39:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么那么做  迪恩\NWhy'd you do it, Dean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.08,0:39:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}做什么\NDo what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.39,0:39:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让我复生\NResurrect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.52,0:39:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可以把我的灵魂随便扔在哪个阴沟里\NYou could have drained my soul into any culvert,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.69,0:39:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也不会有人知道\Nand no one would have been the wiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.03,0:39:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在胡说些什么\NWhat the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.07,0:39:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你没事吧\NHey, you good?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.42,0:39:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}兄弟  我不知道我算个什么东西\NMan... I don't know what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.84,0:40:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好极了\NOh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.39,0:41:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我叫本尼\NI'm Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.38,0:41:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}久仰你的大名了  萨姆\NHeard a lot about you, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.86,0:41:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看得出来你们两个有很多话要说\NI can see you two have a lot to talk about.

